name: Keisha Robinson
summary:
Keisha Robinson is a 31-year-old woman from Chicago, Illinois who currently lives in Los Angeles, California. She is a Production Coordinator in the Entertainment industry and is a graduate of the University of California, Los Angeles. Keisha is 5'7", values integrity, community, and creativity, and enjoys movies, cycling, and traveling.

She is Christian and politically moderate, seeking a long-term, monogamous relationship. She identifies as straight, uses the pronouns She/Her/Hers, and is of Black African descent. She doesn't have children but wants to have them in the future. She has a cat, enjoys the occasional drink but doesn't smoke or use marijuana or drugs.

Keisha prefers a straight man aged between 30 to 40 years, standing 5'8" to 6'3" tall. Her ideal partner would want children, enjoy a drink but abstain from smoking, marijuana, and drugs. Keisha embraces the active lifestyle and appreciates a partner who does the same.
